Extending from our corporate values, exemplify the following:
Empathy – We seek to understand the needs, feelings, and motivations of customers and colleagues.
Pragmatism – We are focused on delivering practical uses and successes, and the business to do, aligned to our strategies and long term direction.
Kaizen – We are focused on continual improvement and learning. We make decisions, we own failures so that we can learn and improve.
Agility – We embrace agility in software development, but first in our ability to change through personal and team behaviors that demonstrate: balance, speed, strength, and coordination.
Kōkua – We seek to help our colleagues and create success for our customers without expecting our own personal gain.
